{"article_id":"rcAnQYu5T0xswfqq","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Yesterday evening , Senate Judiciary Chairman Chuck Grassley","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"( R-Iowa )","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"gave attorney Debra S. Katz an ultimatum","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"- agree to reasonable testimonial terms for her client and alleged sexual assault survivor Professor Christine Blasey Ford by 10:00 PM Friday","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"or the Senate would go ahead","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"and vote on Monday","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"to confirm Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"In return , Katz accused the senator of establishing an `` arbitrary '' deadline","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"and flatly declined to comply with his request","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"and instead asked for one more day .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Shortly after midnight , Sen. Grassley agreed to give Katz and her client one more day .","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"Professor Ford claims","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"that Kavanaugh sexually assaulted her 36 years ago during a high school party ,","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"but has flummoxed for the past week on actual details and if she even wanted to testify .","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"Originally , Professor Ford and her counsel had a 10:00 AM deadline on Friday","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"to submit requests for testimony","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"including date , time , and other specifics .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"That deadline passed .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Then , Sen. Grassley announced on Friday evening","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"was willing to give en more time until the aforementioned 10:00 PM deadline .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"Katz further claimed","depth":3},{"id":21,"text":"that Sen. Grassley displayed a `` cavalier '' treatment '' and `` inappropriate '' behavior towards a sexual assault survivor .","depth":3},{"id":22,"text":"Christine Blasey Ford ' s attorney responds to Senate Judiciary Chair Grassley ' s deadline :","depth":3},{"id":23,"text":"\" Our modest request is that she be given an additional day","depth":4},{"id":24,"text":"to make her decision. \"","depth":4},{"id":25,"text":"pic.twitter.com/Pn537QDanu","depth":4},{"id":26,"text":"- Phil Mattingly","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"( @ Phil_Mattingly )","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"September 22 , 2018","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"Sen. Grassley responded","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"by saying ,","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"`` come to us","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"or we come to you ''","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"and implored Professor Ford to let the Senate judiciary committee know","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"if she was willing to testify or not .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"Five times now we hv granted extension for Dr Ford","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"to decide","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"if she wants to proceed w her desire","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"stated one wk ago","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"that she wants to tell senate her story","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"Dr Ford","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"if u changed ur mind","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"say so","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"so we can move on","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"I want to hear ur testimony .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Come to us","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"or we to u","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"- ChuckGrassley","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"( @ ChuckGrassley )","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"September 22 , 2018","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"After nearly two hours , of no definitive response to Katz 's latest request ,","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"the Senate judiciary chairman tweeted his response","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"saying ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"`` I want to hear her ''","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"and that he had decided to grant another extension .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Judge Kavanaugh I just granted another extension to Dr Ford","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"to decide","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"if she wants to proceed w the statement","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"she made last week","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"to testify to the senate","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"She shld decide","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"so we can move on","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"I want to hear her .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"I hope u understand .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"It ' s not my normal approach to b indecisive","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"- ChuckGrassley","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"( @ ChuckGrassley )","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"September 22 , 2018","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"With all the extensions","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"we give Dr Ford","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"to decide","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"if she still wants to testify to the Senate","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"I feel like","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"I ' m playing 2nd trombone in the judiciary orchestra","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"and Schumer is the conductor","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"- ChuckGrassley","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"( @ ChuckGrassley )","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"September 22 , 2018","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Under this framework , Katz and Professor Ford now have until 10:00 PM tonight","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"to decide","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"if they are willing to testify .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":161,"left":102,"right":160,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":102,"left":100,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":91,"right":99,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":87,"right":90,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":87,"left":83,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":82,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":82,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":3,"right":85,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":4,